Name: Syulen PYAM Exec
Description:
Manufacturer: Gatac Manufacture
Focus: Cargo

The Syulen cargo vessel has been artfully crafted by the renowned House Gatac to be well suited for both Human and Xi’an pilots. With a refined agile frame, the Syulen lends itself to ferrying important deliveries across the universe. This special variant features an exclusive livery and loadout for the ship.
